snippet.title: Elemental Gearbolt - Hyper PlayStation Re-MIX Trailer
snippet.description:
This preview of Elemental Gearbolt was featured on a demo disc of a Japanese magazine Hyper PlayStation Re-MIX. While Sony themselved released the game in Japan, the English release in the US was published by Working Designs. It never saw a PAL release, though.

Elemental Gearbolt (C) Sony Interactive Entertainment
